    "At the same time, this is also the most basic behavioral feature of \"humans\" in HDT.Wang et al. [66] presented an approach to extract a 3D facial model from an image using a shape regression network.",
    "This method obtained high-quality 3D model pictures at minimal cost, and achieved high-accuracy facial modeling.",
    "Although this method is not strictly HDT, it is also the theoretical basis for constituting HDT.",
    "Razzaq et al. [67] used Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN) to build HDT models of students' and teachers' facial expressions and behaviors for remote teaching and classroom supervision.",
